      "narration_text": "Self-demo: Soul Character photo plan and command — free, no training initiated. Subject: NikBearBrown. Step one: gather twelve face photos — frontal, three-quarter, profile, varied lighting. Step two: variant is --soul-2 for image generation. Step three: the training command, with wait. The plan is free. The soul-id create call is paid and gated by the human approving the photo set.",
